componentAttributes.description: Legend Boats orientation videos help teach you everything you need to know about operating your boat.  From launching your boat and loading it on the trailer, installing your boat top, and proper engine trimming to keeping your stuff dry and making sure your boat is always ready for optimal performance, Legend Orientation Videos will ensure you're ready to enjoy your time on the water.
